section_1.title: Section_1_title
content: Hello, My name is Dmitry, I've worked as Web developer since 2010.
I have got experience as front end developer using different java script frameworks - DOJO, ExtJs, React, Angular 4/5.
Of course I've used HTML, CSS, SASS and etc.
Also I've worked as back end developer.
I participated in different project for e-comerce, content management and telecomunication.
I've' used Java 6-8, Spring Framework, AOP, JPA, JMS, different BPM frameworks.
